WITH last_point AS ( SELECT MAX(time) AS last_time FROM ue WHERE time BETWEEN $__timeFrom AND $__timeTo )
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(pci)) FROM ue CROSS JOIN last_point WHERE time >= last_point.last_time - INTERVAL '5s' AND time <= last_point.last_time

WITH last_point AS ( SELECT MAX(time) AS last_time FROM ue WHERE time BETWEEN $__timeFrom AND $__timeTo )
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(rnti)) FROM ue CROSS JOIN last_point WHERE time >= last_point.last_time - INTERVAL '5s' AND time <= last_point.last_time
SELECT time, SUM(dl_brate) FROM ue WHERE time >= $__timeFrom AND time <= $__timeTo GROUP BY time ORDER BY time
SELECT MAX(total_dl_brate) FROM ( SELECT SUM(dl_brate) AS total_dl_brate FROM ue WHERE time >= $__timeFrom AND time <= $__timeTo GROUP BY time ORDER BY time )
SELECT dl_brate, time, pci, rnti FROM ue WHERE time >= $__timeFrom AND time <= $__timeTo ORDER BY time
SELECT ul_brate, time, pci, rnti FROM ue WHERE time >= $__timeFrom AND time <= $__timeTo ORDER BY time
SELECT (100.0 * dl_nof_nok) / (dl_nof_ok + dl_nof_nok), time, pci, rnti FROM ue WHERE time >= $__timeFrom AND time <= $__timeTo ORDER BY time
SELECT (100.0 * ul_nof_nok) / (ul_nof_ok + ul_nof_nok), time, pci, rnti FROM ue WHERE time >= $__timeFrom AND time <= $__timeTo ORDER BY time
